Date: 1999-09-07

Title: Comments on the Moduli Dynamics of 1/4 BPS Dyons

Authors: Dongsu Bak and Kimyeong Lee

Comments: 5 pages

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B468 (1999) 76-80

We rederive the nonrelativistic Lagrangian for the low energy dynamics of 1/4BPS dyons by considering the time dependent fluctuations around classical 1/4BPS configurations. The relevant fluctuations are the zero modes of theunderlying 1/2 BPS monopoles.